<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-9297] The configuration for remote debugging is not valid anymore.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9297</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current configuration for remote debugging that we use is: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;# JVM_OPTS=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$JVM_OPTS -Xdebug -Xnoagent -Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=1414&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since java 1.5 it should be: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;JVM_OPTS=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$JVM_OPTS -agentlib:jdwp=transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=1414&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
